---
// Utterances comment system - free, GitHub Issues based
---

<div class="comments-section">
	<h3>评论</h3>
	<script src="https://utteranc.es/client.js"
		repo="aimeetyi/cetc3bj"
		issue-term="pathname"
		label="comment"
		theme="github-light"
		crossorigin="anonymous"
		async>
	</script>
</div>

<style>
	.comments-section {
		border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1em;
		margin-top: 2em;
	}
	.comments-section h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #333;
		font-size: 1.1em;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
		padding-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
</style>
